title: CCGHQ MTG Pics Update 021014
description:
I was going to roll these updates into the Complete torrent but didn't have time.
So instead I'm releasing an Update torrent. This collection includes a bunch of advertisement cards that won't end up in the regular torrent, so get them now.
Tokens and Emblems are included in the sets but not separately. 
This collection also includes all the Tinys that didn't make it into the Complete torrent.


Included are 1.89 GB of:
DDL (Duel Decks Heroes vs Monsters) 
Face the Hydra
M14 (Magic 2014)
THS (Theros)
V13 (From the Vault 20) in two different scan versions
Tiny Fun Pics

For more see http://www.slightlymagic.net/forum/viewtopic.php?p=145560#p145560
